When downloaded,use PowerISO.Then copy the files from your virtual player to a directory.
Open the "crack-folder" and copy the folders to simular folders in ETKA.
The content in ETKA/ET_PATCH has to be copied to the root of ETKA program.
Then install program using ETKSETUP.EXE
Should work just fine then, good luck:-)
